Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面航路通畅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机凰空母接近 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持直线前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在这里击沉敌舰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就达到阿尔玛达海战的胜利条件了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7}注：\N-----------------------------------\N阿尔玛达海战中撤退战的胜利条件是\N将敌军战舰在三征西班牙领地内击沉\N即敌方在英国境内的战舰即使击沉也不算数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机凰 一号机 出动了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算让机凰出动后空母退至后方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛哥特！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是半龙把我送过来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛哥特 拿好这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有折断还真是万幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以玛哥特 一起来战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来把那架机凰空母击坠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这的途中收到了很有趣的邮件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\pos(638,622)}M.H.R.R
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为跟神圣罗马帝国很近的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}EDEL Brocken\N{\r}「俯瞰魔山」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛哥特 我不是来帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以接下来 一起前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起向着属於魔女的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更高更快地翱翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Verwandlung\N{\r}「镜换装」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\pos(662,620)}Flowlen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.42,0:01:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们跟新制作的「令嬢」缔结召唤契约吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Weiss Flowlen\N{\r}「白嬢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Schwarz Flowlen\N{\r}「黒嬢」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Weiss Flowlen\N{\r}「白嬢」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Zwei Flowlen\N{\r}「双嬢」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)\fs50\pos(351.667,573)}{\fn方正大标宋_GBK}{\4c&H0F0F0F&}{\3c&H0F0F0F&}{\bord1}『越境的贪欲者们』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展翅高飞吧 玛哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾速冲刺吧 小伽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不追去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伽 虽然不明白怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像很厉害 所以上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连空间描写都可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是最新型号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让加速的力量在内部爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使其更进一步加速的准对舰魔术式炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Herrlich\N{\r}不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去追赶之前起飞的机凰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\pos(500.333,623.333)}Zwei Flowlen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「双嬢」第二形态 合体完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要冲过去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把身体压低点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气阻力很大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部的感觉很舒服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Herrlich\N{\r}不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只使用了初始燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样燃料费会大幅增加吧 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的干扰术式符清除作业也差不多结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成确认操作后 请采取安定的防御姿态…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武藏 全舰上升！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始上升 以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是被察觉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在被吃掉之前对方自行沉没的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利条件就不成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来从后方展开追击战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以炮击来诱导武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让主力舰队绕至其后的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武藏的撤退战就无法成立 唯有败北一途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武藏所面对的道路就只剩下两条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条是确保空母的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣称满足胜利条件而结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一条是将所有权利移交英国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由英国进行追击战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 前者的前提与各国之间的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7}注：\N-----------------------------------\N武藏因为被各国所警戒，所以交涉无法成立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后者会使武藏的战斗能力遭到怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个对武藏来说都是地狱般的选择啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能自己想办法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 很 有意思 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看出来这孩子还挺有胆色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托大家一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…隐形障壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要脱离这片海域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃阿尔玛达海战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的武藏是做不到脱离的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该立即就会显形的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 保持监视状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现迹象 立即进行炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Tes.\N{\r}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下方发现舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在隐形状态下让舰船向下方航行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算确保空母残骸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个形状是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运输舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上空出现巨大飞行物体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垂直上升…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空中进行垂直翻转吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米里亚姆 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是运气不好桌子没固定好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八成会被碾死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈呢 因为爸爸被其他女人给睡走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要寻死去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个话题还是不要再提了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边说「跟余好好SEX吧」什么的一边狂敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后可是会被检非违使给抓走的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7}注：检非违使\N-----------------------------------\N平安时代初期的警察司法总监
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能别用那副表情说这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦 和我一起好好抱住这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚也可以掺在一起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都同意了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要绕到圣·马丁的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总长 副王赫莱森 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托利大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗 赫莱森期待着胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有了胜利的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终於和我一样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动「悲叹的怠惰」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大罪的抓痕捕获吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们也露露脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到这边被压制了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别无他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才经由乌尔基亚伽大人从ネ申原大人那拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大罪武装！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「拒绝的强欲」！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超过驱动状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己受到的所有攻击转化为流体储蓄在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变为使用者的内燃拜气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那么在这里可爱得像兔子一样的电池就不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7}注：\N-----------------------------------\N 托利的术式效果是提供流体燃料，这里比喻成电池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里会有先用预备电池的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要先把托利大人给榨光了才行
