Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起取胜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 武藏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽·斯图尔特！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 对我来说是「都铎」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点藏大人 请扶着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Jud.\N{\r}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}E.X.Collbrande\N{\r}「王赐剣一型」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保护我从今开始觉得重要的东西吧！
