Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.20,jpcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs38\3c&H62FF62&\blur1.5\be1\fad(300,300)}繁星祭典之日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:39.83,jpcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs38\3c&H62FF62&\blur1.5\be1\fad(300,300)}歎息數次
